there wasn't nothing there I want to see twice.

00:31.240 --> 00:32.571
DOCTOR: Sit down, Albert.

00:32.658 --> 00:34.489
No, thank you. I'm not tired.

00:34.577 --> 00:36.442
DOCTOR: I didn't say you were.

00:37.663 --> 00:40.120
