weren't what we'd hoped for.

01:14.992 --> 01:16.903
Your cancer has spread to your liver.

01:21.666 --> 01:23.327
I'm sorry, Albert.

01:37.640 --> 01:38.755
Hey.

01:38.849 --> 01:40.180
Let's go.

01:41.102 --> 01:42.808
What happened in there?

01:42.895 --> 01:45.056
