03:30.211 --> 03:31.792
Let's go.

03:34.924 --> 03:37.586
All right, what's going on?

03:40.054 --> 03:41.043
Jennifer?

03:42.223 --> 03:44.134
Cherise's boyfriend got shot, Mr. Batiste.

03:44.225 --> 03:46.261
