03:46.352 --> 03:47.467
Oh, no.

03:48.270 --> 03:49.851
Deron?

03:49.939 --> 03:52.021
-Deron Coleman?
-Cherise was there when they shot him.

03:52.108 --> 03:53.097
What?

03:53.192 --> 03:55.899
She and Deron was walking up the street
and a car rolled up on them.

03:55.986 --> 03:57.066
Cherise wasn't hit, was she?

03:57.154 --> 03:58.143
No, she's all right.

03:58.239 --> 04:00.901
