06:19.797 --> 06:21.207
No.

06:21.298 --> 06:23.209
We lived in a shotgun double.

06:24.260 --> 06:28.378
My grandmam and my family on one side,
my aunts on the other.

06:29.348 --> 06:32.340
-We called it the Lambreaux Estate.
-(LAUGH|NG)

06:36.105 --> 06:42.897
Then my father and his brothers
built this here Creole shotgun for us.

06:43.904 --> 06:49.444
They were all carpenters,
bricklayers, tradesmen.

06:52.955 --> 06:54.240
And the day that it was finished,

06:54.331 --> 06:58.324
the priest came over from Epiphany
and put a branch on the roof.

06:59.420 --> 07:01.160
