07:20.274 --> 07:23.607
Billy liked to have an occasional drink.

07:23.694 --> 07:28.279
And they put a resisting arrest charge
on top of the drunken charge.

07:28.949 --> 07:30.860
Battery of an officer.

07:31.076 --> 07:34.159
