He sure wouldn't bite a man.

07:41.253 --> 07:47.544
A witness at OPP said
they saw Billy having trouble breathing.

07:48.093 --> 07:53.178
He had the asthma since he was a boy.
He kept an inhaler in his pocket all the time.

07:54.725 --> 07:58.138
But they took it from him, didn't they?

07:58.228 --> 07:59.809
Apparently, they did, Mrs. Gilday.

07:59.897 --> 08:02.354
