I think we have the grounds for a lawsuit.

08:16.330 --> 08:17.615
What type of lawsuit?

08:17.706 --> 08:19.162
Wrongful death.

08:19.249 --> 08:20.204
You're gonna be our lawyer?

08:20.292 --> 08:22.499
If you'd like me to be, yes.

08:24.088 --> 08:28.502
